OL,3,CQueen Elizabeth II's official
OL,4,Cbiographer named
OL,6,FHistorian Anna Keay, whose most
OL,7,Fcelebrated book is about Britain's
OL,8,Frepublican period, has been confirmed
OL,9,Fas Queen Elizabeth II's official
OL,10,Fbiographer.
OL,12,FMs Keay will be able to talk to
OL,13,Fmembers of the royal family and the
OL,14,Flate Queen's friends and household
OL,15,Fwhen researching the book, and she
OL,16,Fwill have access to her personal and
OL,17,Fofficial papers held in the Royal
OL,18,FArchives.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
