OL,3,CQueen Elizabeth II's official
OL,4,Cbiographer named
OL,6,FIt was reported last weekend that the
OL,7,FKing wanted a female author for the
OL,8,Ftask and the academic was in talks for
OL,9,Fthe prestigious role.
OL,11,FOfficial royal biographies sometimes
OL,12,Fthrow up unexpected facts or details
OL,13,Fabout the subject's life and shed
OL,14,Flight on important periods.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
