OL,3,CQueen Elizabeth II's official
OL,4,Cbiographer named
OL,6,FMs Keay is a trustee of the Royal
OL,7,FCollection Trust, which the King
OL,8,Fsupports as patron, and is a member of
OL,9,Fthe Queen Elizabeth Memorial Committee.
OL,11,FShe has written a number of books
OL,12,Fabout British history and culture
OL,13,Fincluding The Restless Republic:
OL,14,FBritain Without A Crown, winner of the
OL,15,F2023 Duff Cooper Prize for non-
OL,16,Ffiction, which chronicles the 11 years
OL,17,FBritain was a republic after Charles I
OL,18,Fwas tried and executed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/5
