OL,4,Cbiographer named
OL,6,FThe historian added: "I am deeply
OL,7,Fgrateful to His Majesty the King for
OL,8,Fentrusting me with this responsibility
OL,9,Fand for granting me access to her
OL,10,Fpapers, and will do all I can to do
OL,11,Fjustice to her life and work."
